      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are proud to present this superlative specimen, maintained to an uncompromising standard. This vehicle exhibits a pristine aesthetic and peak mechanical performance, reflecting the highest level of care and preservation. Every surface remains in showroom condition, offering a rare opportunity for the discerning buyer to acquire a vehicle that transcends the typical pre-owned market. Experience the pinnacle of automotive refinement in a package that commands respect on every road.",
